Instruction: With the new battery installed and all switches ON, sequentially measure the DC voltage between the two cables at the interface of each pair of modules: first directly at the PSU output, then at the input of Control Module 1, then at the output of Control Module 1 / input of Control Module 2, and so on up to the input of the load module. This will localize the segment where the 12 V disappears and reveal any miswired or open inter-module connection.
